data.description: Welcome to 931 Johnson Road, a cozy farmhouse on 2.13 acres, perfect for those who want a taste of country living, but be close to all of the amenities in town. With 3 bedrooms and 2.5 bathrooms, it's great for anyone looking for a laid-back lifestyle. Step inside to find an updated kitchen with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, blending farmhouse charm with modern convenience. The open floor plan downstairs creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere, perfect for gatherings and everyday living. Durable luxury vinyl plank flooring adds a stylish yet practical touch throughout the house. Heading upstairs, you'll find the primary suite, offering plenty of closet space and its own private bathroom for a peaceful retreat. Two additional bedrooms provide flexibility for guests, complemented by a guest bathroom for convenience. Outside, there's a classic barn and a 3-bay detached garage, giving you space to tinker with your tools and hobbies. The big lot leaves room for gardens, play areas, or just enjoying the outdoors. Some practical updates to ensure comfort and stability include: a new mound system septic installed in 2021,  HVAC system in 2016, and new roof in 2016. In addition to that, there are solar panels to keep your utility costs down. 931 Johnson Road is more than a home,  it's a chance to experience the simple joys of country life with a touch of modern comfort while still being close to town. If you've been dreaming of a laid-back farmhouse lifestyle, this is your opportunity. Sale includes solar panels & requires purchaser to assume solar panel agreement. Contact listing agent for details.
